      "title": "Norochchole's first generator restored",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A senior official of the Ceylon Electricity Board said that the first power generator of the Lakwijaya Power Plant in Norochchole, which had suffered a sudden breakdown, was restored and connected to the national electricity system.",
        "The official further said that with the addition of this generator to the national grid, a capacity of 300 megawatts was added to the national grid."
      ],
